WingRazor shook her head. "I better stay here, all of our equipement 
is here... we can't let it fall in the wrong hands..."

"I'll stay." Rave smiled pulling out his blasters." You two save our 
buds and i'll play wack a mole with the preds if they think they can 
come in here."

Wing nodded... "Alright... Waith here one second friend, i'll get 
Sabre. She entered the ship and soon emerged with Sabre's limp form 
in her arms...
